data.description: Located just outside of town and nestled in a very private creekside setting sits this beautiful custom home on 3.5 acres with huge views! From the primary bedroom with double walk-in closets, to the lower level screen porch with a hot tub, this home lacks nothing for a destination experience. Open floorplan with hardwood Floors throughout, huge windows for natural light, pass-through natural stone fireplace, split floorplan, main level laundry, and 2 car garage is only a fraction of what this home has to offer. As we move downstairs, you'll have access to a huge bonus space with multi-purpose rooms, a large family room for movie nights, an additional bathroom, and even a built-in music studio. This house has it all. Enjoy entertaining guests on the back porch while soaking in the stars or private nights in the hot tub. The whole-home generator is included to ensure you never lose power. Minutes to Dillsboro shopping and casino. Schedule your private tour today!
